1.3
log
@fix cross references to self; found with mandoc -Tlint
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: SSL_num_renegotiations.3,v 1.2 2017/04/10 14:00:51 schwarze Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2016 Ingo Schwarze <schwarze@@openbsd.org>
